        Open Spin &nbsp;·&nbsp; Virtual Vibes &nbsp;·&nbsp; Warm Samples &nbsp;·&nbsp; Sophist-pop
      </span>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label">The April Rotation</div>

    <table class="schedule">
      <tr>
        <td class="col-date">Apr 02</td>
        <td class="col-dot">◆</td>
        <td class="col-venue">Midwest Sad</td>
        <td class="col-time">7PM – 9PM</td>
        <td class="col-sep">|</td>
        <td class="col-theme">Virtual Vibes</td>
